18 successor or similar document;
19 3. "Domicile" means the country in which a company is
20 registered, the company's affairs are primarily completed, and where
21 the majority of ownership share is held;
22 4. "Federally banned corporation" means any company or
23 designated equipment federally banned currently or banned after the
