1 effe ctive date of this act. Such bans shall include those resulting
2 from, but not limited to, the following federal agencies and acts:
3 a. the Federal Communications Commission, including, but
4 not limited to, any equipment or service deemed to
5 pose a threat to national security identified on the
6 Covered List developed pursuant to 47 C.F.R., Section
7 1.50002 and published by the Public Safety and
