11 Section 1601 et seq.,
12 b. the United States Department of Commerce,
13 c. the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency,
14 d. the Federal Acquisition Security Council, and
15 e. Section 889 of the John S. McCain National Defense
16 Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2019, P. L. 115-232;
17 5. "Foreign adversary" means adversarial nations including the
18 People's Republic of China, the Russian Federation, the Islamic
19 Republic of Iran, the Democratic People's Republic of Korea, the
20 Republic of Cuba, the Venezuelan regime of Nicolás Maduro, and the
21 Syrian Arab Republic, including any agent of or any other entity
